genresAdvancedInfo.name: vintage italian pop
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Vintage Italian Pop - This genre of music emerged in the 1950s and 1960s in Italy and is characterized by its upbeat and catchy melodies. It often features orchestral arrangements and romantic lyrics that reflect the optimism and joy of post-war Italy.
